a co-op game (and I grew up playing co-op games.) Highly recommended. Out on Nintendo Switch now. Grab a buddy or two and get this game. No wonder it’s a solid 10/10 on Steam!</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Lovers in a Dangerous Spacetime","date":"December 22, 2017"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/2017-12-22-lovers-in-a-dangerous-spacetime","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/posts/2016-07-16-why-im-not-playing-pokmon-go","type":"post"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Why I'm Not Playing Pokémon Go"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/posts/2018-02-07-9-satra","type":"post"},"frontmatter":{"title":"9 Satra"}}}}